original: Bjerkhagen, Roland Alf Robert, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 19/4/09 i Gbg. G. 38 m. Beth Fredrikson. Barn: Agneta f. 40, Anders 42, Eva 47. — Stud:-ex. v. Gbgs h. real 29, Cand. med. dent. i Greifswald 31, stud. i Wien 31-32, tysk tandl. 33, sv. dito 35. Prakt, i Nor- berg 35, i Gbg sed. 35, skoltandl. v. Mölndals folksk. 37-42.
translated: Bjerkhagen, Roland Alf Robert, dentist, Gothenburg, born April 19, 1909 in Gothenburg. Married in 1938 to Beth Fredrikson. Children: Agneta born in 1940, Anders in 1942, Eva in 1947. He graduated from Gothenburg High School in 1929, got a degree in dentistry from Greifswald in 1931, studied in Vienna from 1931 to 1932, worked as a German dentist in 1933 and Swedish dentist in 1935. He worked as a dentist in Norberg in 1935, and in Gothenburg since 1935. He also worked as a school dentist at Mölndals Folkskola from 1937 to 1942.
